name: Moon Wedding Animated Book Page
description:
Moon Wedding, Big Big Book Page 1992-1995, Mm Collage on Canvas
I animated it using Light Tricks and edited it with sound in Kinemaster.

This NFT features the music of Cu-Out “ Spring Collection” 
Cut-Out is a studio project by members of Pell Mell, Robert Beerman, Greg Freeman and Steve Fisk. This music is unreleased and is being used by permission.
